Class WorkLoad

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.WorkLoadDescription
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.WorkLoad
public class WorkLoad extends WorkLoadDescription
WorkLoad creates an object, given an input file, containing information that will be used to measure the graphs efficiency.
